{"tid":507350,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］毒撚聖誕歌 啲丫精 - 今晚我注定手淫","createTime":"2017-12-23T07:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T07:14:16.000Z","uid":45331,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"168f4457bc246376f924df72a5319b6fd0ae36b6","tid":507350,"uid":45331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:08:10.000Z","msg":"看 看著你的臉 播著薄格片<br />\n毒癮在膀胱蔓延<br />\n我 快射到痴線 五十個缺點<br />\n滿面濃瘡彷彿給我加冕<br />\n<br />\n不管燈飾多普遍 得我電視幕前<br />\n一聲不發拔出寶劍<br />\n<br />\n今晚我注定手淫 我太毒尚有抱枕<br />\n一分鐘發射可能 聖誕夜是種遺憾<br />\n簡單一碌棍 手心的抖震<br />\n示意我看AV不需紙巾<br />\n收卡說「你是好人」 永遠沒性的光棍<br />\n再回望這生 哪有女陪襯<br />\n一個勿呻吟 搵外快情人 不想單身<br />\n<br />\n從來不相信一生不愛侶 遺留雙手一對<br />\n別再等 別再等 但我的積蓄得幾百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e79a55ec8b63bd627e6401d0c57ac54c82bcd1e","tid":507350,"uid":158332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d843f266742f9648a7c75131cfe233999c13c3","tid":507350,"uid":45331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T17:52:13.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259ed465d8ebaab46e3818a444df60f7cd956ba8","tid":507350,"uid":45331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"連登無毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cfb050953ae1f9189694beefa43f77ee91ea08","tid":507350,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"見樓豬咁慘 等我住你聖誕有著落啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d3663b4776ce0145fcdece825d6a5d74c716aa","tid":507350,"uid":39567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"